1
00:00:04,750 --> 00:00:07,590
(What is wrong with me...? Seriously!)

2
00:00:08,630 --> 00:00:12,800
You seem a little off today, Makoto.
Are you okay?

3
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:15,850
(It's because you're acting like nothing happened...!)

4
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,060
So, what are we practicing today?

5
00:00:23,210 --> 00:00:25,610
You're getting really good at doing your own makeup.

6
00:00:25,610 --> 00:00:29,820
Mhm, you did a great job today.
It looks good.

7
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:34,120
Oh! Really? That's awesome!

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:36,870
You're cute, Makoto.

9
00:00:36,870 --> 00:00:40,000
Cu...? What?

10
00:00:41,250 --> 00:00:43,880
Huh? No one's ever said that to me before.

11
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:46,330
The classic princely look is great,

12
00:00:46,330 --> 00:00:49,340
but I think you could totally pull off a 'cute' style too.

13
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:52,050
Oh, so that's what you meant.

14
00:00:52,260 --> 00:00:55,140
(Am I just overthinking this...?)

15
00:00:55,140 --> 00:00:56,890
(Is he not thinking about it at all?)

16
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:59,480
(After what happened between us...)

17
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:03,810
(Why do I keep replaying that in my head...?!)

18
00:01:03,810 --> 00:01:06,820
(Play it cool... Just be cool.)

19
00:01:13,030 --> 00:01:17,580
Yuki-kun! Long time no see!
